{"tid":421390,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"依家d 90好無知，以為大陸仲用緊現金，人地已經領先香港好多了！","createTime":"2017-10-02T08:04:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-19T04:54:28.000Z","uid":19334,"like":12,"dislike":109,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"ed1bd549d97d53210563a33187353c10962abf58","tid":421390,"uid":19334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T08:04:06.000Z","msg":"話說中秋前有個conference dinner邀請左我同90後，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我就約左佢係上水等，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我地轉緊車去羅湖果陣，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢突然問我唱左幾多人仔，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我當堂嚇一跳，然後得啖笑，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係人都知中國資訊好發達，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲用緊八達通同現金咩！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好多野都已經轉哂做電子支付（微信/支付寶），<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就算一個師奶去買餸都用緊電子支付，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n連銀包都唔洗拎，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁點解仲要唱人仔！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢依家先去開番個銀行戶口實名認證！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無知真係好恐怖！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17c4721a112e35a794d7172f157c052076cd88c4","tid":421390,"uid":116530,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T08:06:11.000Z","msg":"支付寶方便咁多 仲唱人仔 咩年代呀"},{"pid":"bbaed2a6c8f73994e4927c62c005090e9f80d317","tid":421390,"uid":19334,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T08:07:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支付寶方便咁多 仲唱人仔 咩年代呀</blockquote>